item.title: Little help please
item.dc:creator: @sheercoldpvp sheercoldpvp
item.description:
@sheercoldpvp wrote:

alright go into your server files,

once there go into your server folder, then io, then login.java (notepad labeled login)

search for p.rights

then look for if ((p.username.equals

then change the name that is in that to your in-game name on your server

NOTE: dont use capitalization, or spacing sometimes errors

then just save that, and compile the server and restart it

have fun
